&lt;p&gt;1개의 아세트산과 1개의 에틸알콜올을 가열하면, &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;C&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}COOH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.07153em;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 와 &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}OH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 사이의 반응으로 물이 제거되면서 에스테르 화합물인 에틸아세테이트가 생성되며, 반응은 더 이상 진행되지 않고 정지된다.
&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;&quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/f2bd9/Polymerization2.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 21.199586349534645%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAjUlEQVQY03VP7QoDIQzz/Z9SRP+oiIie33ZL4QYbt0KVJmmbCnrHnJP23vQU55yveq31V4sQeLTW1FpjYUqJM8ZIvXcWgfPe0xiDQgjMQYtlwK7rYhx9AmDOmZxzTECAGvjtDs0YDnelFB4IDTBwuBAcfgESDpG3I2BKKR7+e761lrVSSqq1fjhjDC95AZcOOAePvPJbAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;Polymerization2&quot;
        title=&quot;Polymerization2&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/799d3/Polymerization2.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/00d96/Polymerization2.png 148w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/0b23c/Polymerization2.png 295w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/799d3/Polymerization2.png 590w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/2a3d6/Polymerization2.png 885w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/f2bd9/Polymerization2.png 967w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
